com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities

Class BulkSiteLinkAdExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.internal.bulk.entities.MultiRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BulkSiteLinkAdExtension

  • public class BulkSiteLinkAdExtension
extends MultiRecordBulkEntity
    Represents a sitelink ad extension that is derived from BulkEntity and can be read or written in a bulk file. Properties of this class and of classes that it is derived from, correspond to fields of the Sitelink Ad Extension record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Sitelink Ad Extension at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=620236.

    The Sitelink Ad Extension record includes the distinct properties of the BulkSiteLink class, combined with the commmon properties of the BulkSiteLinkAdExtension class, for example getAccountId() and getSiteLinksAdExtension().

    One BulkSiteLinkAdExtension has one or more BulkSiteLink. Each BulkSiteLink instance corresponds to one Sitelink Ad Extension record in the bulk file. If you upload a BulkSiteLinkAdExtension, then you are effectively replacing any existing site links for the sitelink ad extension.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
